contentrichtext.text: '''ICIS''' can refer to: *[[Integrated Cadastral Information Society]], a non-profit organization *[[International Conference on Information Systems]], an annual academic conference in [[Information Systems]] *[[Idaho National Laboratory|Instrumentation, Control and Intelligent Systems]], a distinctive signature organization in the Idaho National Laboratory *[[Institute for Security and Cooperation in Space]], a non-profit organization *[[Internal Counter-Intelligence Service]], a fictional organization in the [[Whoniverse|Doctor Who universe]] {{Disambig}}
